videoData.title: The upside of data

nodes.whoTheyAre: Jessica Donohue directs an innovative partnership that unites financial theory and practice as a senior vice president and head of the research and advisory business at State Street Global Exchange. She and her team capitalize on their exclusive blend of academic and industry knowledge to provide solutions that enhance returns, control risk, optimize performance, manage liquidity, and monitor market conditions. Donohue’s published research on investor behavior provides the foundation for some of State Street’s proprietary indicators.

videoData.description: Jessica Donohue examines what she's learned from her career working with data, how old industry lessons still apply as we enter the era of Big Data, and why passion still (and always) matters when it comes to data analysis.
